"glavnog prozora traje predugo, možda biste trebali isporobati drugu pozadinu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:773
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Ruleset Editor</title>"
msgstr "<title>Editor pravilnika</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:775
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Ruleset Editor</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Editor pravilnika</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:780
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Ruleset Editor</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Editor pravilnika</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:783
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the Ruleset Editor to customize rulesets. Predefined rulesets are shown "
"in an italic font, customized rulesets have a normal font. Predefined "
"rulesets cannot be changed by the user in any way, however an update of "
"&kajongg; might. Customized rulesets will never be affected by an update."
msgstr ""
"Koristite editor pravilnika da podesite pravilnike. Predefinisani pravilnici "
"su prikazani u italic fontu, podešeni pravilnici u normalnom fontu. "
"Predefinisani pravilnici ne mogu biti promijenjeni od strane korisnika na "
"bilo koji način, međutim ažuriranje &kajongg;-a može. Ažuriranje nikada neće "
"uticati na podešene pravilnike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:785
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When starting a new game, you will be able to select a ruleset for that "
"game. All rulesets defined in the ruleset editor can be used. The ruleset is "
"saved together with the game, so you can always change rulesets here - your "
"changes will only affect future games."
msgstr ""
"Kada počinjete novu igru, bit će moguće da odaberete pravilnik za tu igru. "
"Svi pravlinici definisani u editoru pravilnika mogu biti korišteni. "
"Pravilnik je spremljen zajedno sa igrom, pa uvijek možete promijeniti "
"pravilnik ovdje - vaše promejene će uticatisamo na buduće igre."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:788
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rule, Points, x2, Limits"
msgstr "Pravilo, Poeni, x2, Ograničenja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:788
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Simply double click on whatever you want to change. If all values are "
"cleared, this rule will have no influence on the game. Rules cannot be "
"deleted."
msgstr ""
"Jednostavno dva puta klinite na bilo šta što želite promijeniti. Ako su sve "
"vrijednosti obrisane, ovo pravilo nema uticaja na igru. Pravila ne mogu biti "
"obrisana."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:793
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy and Remove"
msgstr "Kopiraj i ukloni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:793
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can copy and remove entire rulesets."
msgstr "Možete kopirati i ukloniti pravilnike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:795
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Again this can even be done if existing games use this ruleset since every "
"game has its own ruleset copy. You can view rulesets for old games: <link "
"linkend=\"game-menu-scoreGame\">Load</link> the old game and <link linkend="
"\"view-explain-scores\">show its score table</link>."
msgstr ""
"Opet ovo može biti urađeno ako postoječa igra koristi ovaj pravilnik pošto "
"svaka igra ima svoju kopiju pravilnika. Možete vidjeti pravilnike za stare "
"igre : <link linkend=\"game-menu-scoreGame\">Učitaj</link>  staru igru i "
"<link linkend=\"view-explain-scores\">prikaži njenu tabelu bodova</link>."

